high_descs: Walk to the table with knives and a phone.
Pick up the butter knife from the front of the table.
Turn right and walk across the room, then turn right to face the apple on the counter.
Cut the apple into three pieces.
Turn right and walk to the trash can.
Put the knife in the trash can.
Turn left and walk across the refrigerator to the counter with the cut apple.
Pick up a piece of apple from the counter.
Turn around and walk to the microwave.
Put the piece of apple in the microwave and heat it.  Take the piece of apple out of the microwave.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn right to walk to the trash can.
Put the piece of apple in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated piece of apple in the trash can.

high_descs: Walk forward and the left past the table and then turn left to face the table.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Turn right and walk across the room and then turn right to face the apple on the counter.
Cut the apple on the counter into 3 pieces.
Turn right, walk past the fridge and turn right to face the trash can.
Place the knife in the trash can.
Turn left and walk across the room and turn right to face the apple on the counter.
Pick up a piece of the apple on the counter.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the microwave on the counter.
Heat the apple piece in the microwave and then remove it.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn right and walk forward past the fridge, then turn left to face the trash can.
Put the apple piece in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: To heat a piece of apple and place it in the trash can.
